            </div>
            <div class="jp-text">
              <h4>AI Without Prompt Engineering</h4>
              <p><code>by llm()</code> replaces entire function bodies. Your type signature is the specification. Jac generates the optimal prompt automatically. Research shows 3.2x faster task completion.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="jac-pillar reveal delay-1">
            <div class="jp-icon">
